LabForge MVP (Version 1.0)
Objective

Develop a desktop application capable of automatically deploying a fully functional Windows Active Directory environment on a Hyper-V host from a declarative configuration file.

The MVP focuses on deployment automation, not long-term infrastructure management.

Success Criteria

A user can launch LabForge, configure a small business environment, review the deployment plan, and automatically provision the entire environment with minimal manual intervention.

